by


v |- mu ; e --> mu' ; e'
------------------------------------------ :: eval
v |- mu; F[e]  --> mu'; F[e']

-------------------------- :: ctx
v |- mu; ctx --> mu; v

-------------------------- :: var
v |- mu; var n --> mu; lookup v n 

v,,v1 |- mu; e2  --> mu'; e2'
------------------------------------------ :: merger
v |- mu; v1 ,, e2  -->   mu'; v1 ,, e2'

--------------------------------------  :: closure
v |- mu; \A.e --> mu; <v, \A.e>

-------------------------------------------------  :: beta
